<TD>
</TD>
<TD>
I will confirm every registration through e-mail (or regular mail if you do not have an e-mail address). If you have not received confirmation in a reasonable time after sending in your registration please send me e-mail asking if I have received your registration.
</TD>
</TR>
<TR>
<TD>
